'''Acimed''' (''Journal of Information Professionals in Health'') is a [[Spanish language]] [[scientific journal|journal]] of [[medical informatics]] published by the National Center of Information on Medical Sciences in [[Cuba]]. It was first published in 1993 and is the first Spanish language journal to be published on the subject of medical informatics.
