{{Refimprove|date=March 2012}} '''Dietitians of Canada''' ('''DC''') is the [[professional organization]] and "nation-wide voice of [[dietitians]] in [[Canada]]".<ref>[http://www.dietitians.ca/ Dietitians of Canada]</ref> As an organization DC is active at the local, provincial, national and international levels and has 6000 members which meet their academic and experience standards. DC is the accrediting body for all university and training programs that credential dietitians to practice in Canada.
