'''E. Theodore Agard''' was an American [[medical physicist]] and a former director of the [[Flower Hospital Oncology Center]]. Originally from Barbados, he earned a master's degree in physics from the [[University of London]], specifically the [[Middlesex Hospital Medical School]] division of the [[University of London]], and a Ph.D. from the [[University of Toronto]] in the same field. He was a believer in [[creationism]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.answersingenesis.org/articles/isd/theo-agard|title=E. Theo Agard|publisher=Answers in Genesis|accessdate=October 2, 2013}}</ref> 

